igned and organized so your resume looks like a work of art. </p> </div> <div class="col d-none d-sm-block"> <div class="mr-auto"> <img data-aos="fade-up" src="assets/images/Icon2.svg" alt="Icon2" style="height: 400px;margin-left: 4rem" class="img-responsive w-100"> </div> </div> </div> <div class="row feature-4 pt-5 feature-4-1" data-aos="fade-up"> <div class="col m-auto"> <img src="assets/images/Icon3.svg" alt="Icon3" class="mobile-screenshot img-responsive w-100 my-5"> <h2 data-aos="fade-up" class="font-700 font-22px">Effortless and Interactive</h2> <p data-aos="fade-up" class="font-18px">We’ve built an interactive user interface that can design a professional CV from scratch using the details provided by you. You can add, remove the sections as your wish and further customize your resume, picking from multiple color combinations. Also you can download or share the resume with anyone directly, easy enough?</p> </div> <div class="col d-none d-sm-block"> <div class="mr-auto"> <img data-aos="fade-up" src="assets/images/Icon3.svg" alt="Icon3" style="height: 400px;margin-left: 4rem" class="img-responsive w-100"> </div> </div> </div> <div class="row my-5"> <div class="col-sm-12 center mb-5"> <h2 class="h1 text-dark font-32px p-0 font-700" data-aos="fade-up">Multiple templates</h2> <p class="kfeatures-p text-dark font-24px" data-aos="fade-up">Making a difference one resume at a time</p> </div> <div class="col-md-12" data-aos="fade-up"> <div class="row resume_templates"> </div> <div class="text-center my-3" id="load_more_templates"> <a class="button button__main button_load_templates m-auto text-white d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" href="./templates.html" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400" data-aos-offset="0"> Load more templates </a> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="container kfeatures"> <div class="row"> <div class="col center"> <h2 class="h1 pt-3 font-32px font-700" data-aos="fade-up">Key Features</h2><!-- <p class="kfeatures-p" data-aos="fade-up">Making a difference one resume at a time</p> --> </div> </div> <div class="row kfeatures-row-1"> <div class="col-sm-4 kfeatures-block"> <div class="" data-aos="fade-up"><img src="assets/images/Icons svg/edit.svg" alt="Easy Resume Builder"></div> <h3 class="h2 font-22px font-700" data-aos="fade-up">Easy Resume Builder</h3> <p data-aos="fade-up" class="font-18px">Create an outstanding professional resume and increase your chances of getting hired.</p> </div> <div class="col-sm-4 kfeatures-block"> <div> <div class="" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200"><img src="assets/images/Icons svg/resume.svg" alt="Multiple Resume
